{"tid":2140588,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發：日本埼玉縣及神戶市停用TikTok帳戶","createTime":"2020-08-05T05:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T07:36:03.000Z","uid":48040,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76c511246c0bd57ae9688e39363eb520fa759b94","tid":2140588,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"據《產經新聞》報道，TikTok 在日本頗受年輕人歡迎， 日本多個縣政府本來都跟北京字節跳動科技有合作協議，會透過 TikTok 發布各種消息，例如新冠肺炎疫情資訊、景點及文化訊息等。<br />\n<br />\n不過近日基於民眾對 TikTok 的私隱安全疑慮，埼玉縣政府及神戶市政府都宣布，停用 TikTok 發佈消息，直至疑慮完全消失。至於大阪府與廣島縣則暫時未有停用 TikTok，但表示會因應日本政府的動向慎重作出反應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2715059/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9F%BC%E7%8E%89%EF%BC%8E%E7%A5%9E%E6%88%B6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8%20TikTok%20%E6%8A%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E8%A2%AB%E7%AB%8A%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2715059%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259F%25BC%25E7%258E%2589%25EF%25BC%258E%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%2520TikTok%2520%25E6%258A%2596%25E9%259F%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25AB%258A%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2585%25AE&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeahY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=adc0a8a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2715059/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9F%BC%E7%8E%89%EF%BC%8E%E7%A5%9E%E6%88%B6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8%20TikTok%20%E6%8A%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E8%A2%AB%E7%AB%8A%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE</a><br />\n<br />\n推到各國跟風<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/eaglenews_hk/status/1290863377678389248?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feaglenews_hk%2Fstatus%2F1290863377678389248%3Fs%3D21&d=Iz1eZ%2F